init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Or just a figment of your imagination?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You take a deep breath and say "I order you to sting me."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You feel a slight stinging sensation on your neck.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You feel the fear slowly dissipating again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It flies off your shoulder and lands on your hand.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are now at peace with the bee and decide to let it fly away.
